1) Create an useful file in each directory
Useful file means collect for each value of ion-dipole distance the energy (theta)
r_theta_extract.py: must be placed in al lthe  l_* folders, it takes all the  *_deg/computed.dat and 
                    *_deg/theory.dat files and create an output file r_theta.csv:
                    r_val_1 , theta_1, nrg_theory, nrg_computed
                    r_val_1 , theta_2, nrg_theory, nrg_computed
                                     ...
                    r_val_2 , theta_1, nrg_theory, nrg_computed  and so on


